connection.py
    classes: Server, Client
        Server:
            is performin
            __init__(port)  opens socket and listens to clients
            run()           deals with search requests

        Client:
            __init__(...)   opens socket, connects to server and sets up the server
            search([{question, lang, id}]) sends queries to server and waits for response
            stop(stop_server) stops client and/or server

